### Hadith 4:470

*Narrated Sahl bin Sad:*

The Prophet said, "Verily! 70,000 or 700,000 of my followers will enter
Paradise altogether; so that the first and the last amongst them will
enter at the same time, and their faces will be glittering like the
bright full moon."

